data.description: Discover your dream home nestled in a serene country setting with breathtaking water and mountain views. This stunning 5-bedroom, 3-bath, 2 car garage house offers an abundance of space and features that will exceed your expectations. Upon entering the large foyer, you'll be greeted by the timeless elegance of this home. Boasting two fireplaces with gas inserts, solid wood cabinets in the kitchen, built-ins throughout, and a formal dining room, this home radiates both comfort and sophistication.The spacious living quarters on both floors provide versatility and convenience for multi-generational living or hosting guests. With a workshop in the basement and ample storage throughout the house, you'll have plenty of space for all your needs.Step outside onto the large deck or relax in the front breezeway sitting area while enjoying the tranquil ambiance and observing the abundant wildlife that surrounds you. The double lot provides ample outdoor space, perfect for entertaining guests or simply enjoying some quiet time. Sit back and relax in your own private courtyard and absorb the suns rays.Located in a prime location with water frontage on Cherokee Lake, this property also presents an excellent opportunity for vacation rental by owner (VRBO). Imagine your guests experiencing the beauty of this location firsthand.Don't miss out on this solidly built home that offers endless possibilities. This home is ready to accommodate your unique lifestyle. Experience luxury living at its finest in this remarkable property.
